

=Bio=

'Lauren works closely with the community and think tank that comprises the economic experiment of The MetaCurrency Project.  In addition to exploring the Future of Money in the field of financial innovation, Lauren has apprenticed with currency designers and new economy thinkers to develop alternative and complementary currencies, metrics, and incentive systems. These systems aid organizations and communities worldwide in measuring, sharing, and acknowledging different forms of tangible and intangible flows of value that are building the New Economy.

Lauren is currently interested in collaborating with communities working in economic development and currency systems worldwide that are building regenerative new economies. Particularly, those focused on supporting currency experiments and reframing new models of capital and monetary exchange within the world of art and culture.

She consults with organizations and offers workshops to help inspire and develop these new systems."
(http://flavors.me/laurenhiggins#580/custom_plain)


